  <div class="comment-content">

    <div class="edit-comment-hide">
      <div class="js-comment-body comment-body markdown-body markdown-format">
          <p>As an example blipfoto mails look like this to me:</p>

<pre><code>  Subject: =?utf-8?Q?Blipfoto=20=2D=20Introducing=20the=20all=2Dnew=20Bli
</code></pre>

<p>Clearly that's a UTF-8-encoded subject, and it needs to be decoded prior to display.</p>
