    <span class="comment-header-right">
        <a href="#issuecomment-21289882" class="comment-header-date"><time class="js-relative-date" datetime="2013-07-20T00:51:38-07:00" title="2013-07-20 00:51:38">July 20, 2013</time></a>
    </span>
  </div> <!-- /.comment-header -->

  <div class="comment-content">

    <div class="edit-comment-hide">
      <div class="js-comment-body comment-body markdown-body markdown-format">
          <p>Annoyingly calling convert on these will show a result like this:</p>

<pre><code>   Subject: =?utf-8?Q?Blipfoto - Introducing the all-new Blipfoto newslett
</code></pre>

<p>So we need to do two things:</p>

<ul>
<li>Decode.</li>
<li>Remove the leading encoding charset and trailing "?="</li>
</ul>
