    <div class="edit-comment-hide">
      <div class="js-comment-body comment-body markdown-body markdown-format">
          <p>I wonder if replacing mimetic is not the only option : no rfc2047 support, more or less stalled development, strict header parsing... <br>
Then, you're the one to choose, while I'd gladly try to move to GMime, I must admit my C++ skills are rudimentary and the resulting code would probably be bad.</p>
